# Lynx Style Sheet (LSS) for Mutt
#
# This file defines the colors for different HTML tags.
#
# The format is:
#
# style <tag> <foreground> <background> <attributes>
#
# Where:
#   <tag> is the HTML tag name (e.g., h1, p, a)
#   <foreground> is the foreground color
#   <background> is the background color
#   <attributes> is a comma-separated list of attributes (e.g., bold, underline)

# Default text
style p green black

# Headings
style h1 brightred black bold
style h2 green black bold
style h3 yellow black bold
style h4 blue black bold
style h5 magenta black bold
style h6 cyan black bold

# Links
style a brightblue black underline

# Visited links
style a.visited magenta black underline

# Images
style img cyan black

# Preformatted text
style pre green black

# Blockquotes
style blockquote yellow black
